methods.name: public String getXMLVersion()
methods.comment:
* Returns the current value of the version property.
     *
     * @return the current value of the version property.
     *
     * @see #setXMLVersion

methods.name: public String getEncoding()
methods.comment:
* Returns the current value of the encoding property.
     *
     * @return the current value of the encoding property.
     *
     * @see #setEncoding

methods.name: public void setXMLVersion(String version)
methods.comment:
* Assigns the current value of the version property.
     *
     * @param version the new "version" value
     * @see #getXMLVersion

methods.name: public void setEncoding(String encoding)
methods.comment:
* Assigns the current value of the encoding property.
     *
     * @param encoding the new "encoding" value
     * @see #getEncoding
